-- Al-Hokair Tourism, MS Retail Sign Agreement to Open Saudi Stores
-- B y   G l e n   C a r e y
-- 2012-06-11T15:13:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-11/al-hokair-tourism-ms-retail-sign-agreement-to-open-saudi-stores.html
Abdul Mohsen Al-Hokair Tourism and
Development Co., a Saudi entertainment group, and MS Retail KSC
of Kuwait signed a memorandum of understanding to open BAROUE
brand stores in  Saudi Arabia. (SABIC)   The agreement is valued at 80 million riyals ($21 million),
the adviser and arranger,  International Financial Advisors (IFA)  KSCC,
said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Glen Carey in Riyadh at 
 gcarey8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew J. Barden at 
 barden@bloomberg.net  